last_episode_to_air.name: Without Reservations
last_episode_to_air.overview: Frankie and Face visit Murdock at his job in a restaurant, and all three become hostages of mobsters out to kill a patron, the US Attorney General.

name: The A-Team
overview: A fictional group of ex-United States Army Special Forces personnel work as soldiers of fortune while on the run from the Army after being branded as war criminals for a "crime they didn't commit".

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Sent to prison by a military court for a crime they didn't commit, these four commandos escaped from a maximum-security stockade and now survive in the Los Angeles underground as soldiers of fortune. So, if you have a problem and there's no one else who can help, and if you think you can find them, maybe you can hire The A-Team.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Pile into that famous black van for another season of adrenaline-pumping adventure with Hannibal, Face, Murdock and B.A. as they fight for justice against dangerous criminals, while staying one step ahead of their archenemy, Colonel Decker.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: In the most popular season ever, Hannibal, Face, Murdock and B.A. face off against new criminals with the most outrageous schemes yet - from toxic-waste dumping to wild-game poaching to restaurant sabotage.

seasons.name: Season 4
seasons.overview: Team up again with B.A., Hannibal, Murdock and Face as they take on hardhearted kidnappers, corrupt millionaires, ruthless drug dealers, and even a Mob kingpin.

seasons.name: Season 5
seasons.overview: B.A., Hannibal, Murdock and Face confront their greatest challenges yet when the mysterious General Stockwell joins them to battle bad guys that include hitmen, hijackers, and mercenary monks.

episodes.name: Mexican Slayride (1)
episodes.overview: Newspaper reporter, Amy Allen, sets out to prove the A-Team really exists and ends up hiring them to rescue one of her fellow reporters whose been kidnapped by Mexican outlaws.

episodes.name: Mexican Slayride (2)
episodes.overview: Part 2 of the pilot episode in which the A-Team have been captured by a group of guerillas and the gang leader they were sent to fight. In the final battle they are assisted by the villagers and with their help, the A-Team is able to overthrow the guerillas, save the reporter and make their way home. Once home, Amy Allen blackmails her way onto the team.

episodes.name: Children of Jamestown
episodes.overview: After the A-Team rescues a girl from a crazed cult leader, they are captured by the man's followers and made the quarry of a death hunt.

episodes.name: Pros and Cons
episodes.overview: B.A.'s friend is held in a prison where the warden holds fight-to-the-death-boxing matches whose winner receives short-lived freedom.

episodes.name: A Small and Deadly War
episodes.overview: Hannibal plays cat and mouse with a renegade S.W.A.T. A-Team that's committing murders for hire.

episodes.name: Black Day at Bad Rock
episodes.overview: While treating a seriously wounded B.A., a suspicious small town doctor notifies the sheriff, who fears that B.A. may be part of a biker gang returning to free its jailed leader.

episodes.name: The Rabbit Who Ate Las Vegas
episodes.overview: The A-Team gets involved in a mob power play when two girls ask them to find their college professor who went to Las Vegas with a perfect gambling system and never came back.

episodes.name: The Out-of-Towners
episodes.overview: The A-Team takes up the cause of New York shopkeepers against neighborhood protection racketeers.

episodes.name: Holiday in the Hills
episodes.overview: B.A.'s fear of flying is justified when the A-Team's plane crashes in the backwoods where they must battle mountain men to keep a man from being burned at the stake.

episodes.name: West Coast Turnaround
episodes.overview: The A-Team delivers produce to the market for a farmer who is slowly being driven out of business by a land-hungry rancher.

episodes.name: One More Time
episodes.overview: The US government recruits the A-Team to rescue a general and his daughter from guerillas in Borneo.

episodes.name: Till Death Do Us Part
episodes.overview: The A-Team has to rescue a reluctant bride being forced to marry her late father's business partner.

episodes.name: The Beast from the Belly of a Boeing
episodes.overview: Hannibal's plan to free a hijacked airborne 747 requires a bit of adjustment when B.A. becomes cataleptic and Murdock temporarily blinded.

episodes.name: A Nice Place to Visit
episodes.overview: The A-Team comes to the aid of a small town being terrorized by a murderous family.

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: Sent to prison by a military court for a crime they didn't commit, these four commandos escaped from a maximum-security stockade and now survive in the Los Angeles underground as soldiers of fortune. So, if you have a problem and there's no one else who can help, and if you think you can find them, maybe you can hire The A-Team.

episodes.name: Diamonds 'n Dust
episodes.overview: The A-Team agrees to transport explosives to a Zimbabwe diamond mine after the owner dies trying to do it himself.

episodes.name: Recipe for Heavy Bread
episodes.overview: The cook from the A-Team's POW camp gives them a tip about a drug deal between the camp's former commander and a prisoner who had sold out to him.

episodes.name: The Only Church in Town
episodes.overview: Face convinces the A-Team to take his case when he receives his fraternity pin in a package from Ecuador from a woman who disappeared from his life fifteen years earlier.

episodes.name: Bad Time on the Border
episodes.overview: Hannibal goes undercover as an illegal alien when the A-Team is asked to find a sick woman who was apparently left behind by alien smugglers.

episodes.name: When You Comin' Back, Range Rider? (1)
episodes.overview: The A-Team must duck their Army pursuers as they try to stop wild horse rustlers.

episodes.name: When You Comin' Back, Range Rider? (2)
episodes.overview: With Decker hot on their heels, the A-Team must try and find of evidence of the mustangs’ illegal rustling as quickly as possible, before they are captured themselves. With enemies coming from two sides, it is ultimately up to Murdock to save his friends.

episodes.name: The Taxicab Wars
episodes.overview: A small cab company hires the A-Team to thwart the sabotage efforts of a larger company trying to run them out of business.

episodes.name: Labor Pains
episodes.overview: The A-Team helps migrant workers to organize against a landowner that is forcing them to live and work under slave-labor conditions.

episodes.name: There's Always a Catch
episodes.overview: The A-Team must once again duck Decker as they try to stop an extortionist plaguing a small fishing village.

episodes.name: Water, Water Everywhere
episodes.overview: A land developer is trying to run three disabled Vietnam vets off the desert property they're renovating.

episodes.name: Steel
episodes.overview: The A-Team looks into sabotage at a construction site.

guest_stars.character: Mobster Tommy Tillis / Crazy Tommy T
guest_stars.name: Michael Baseleon

episodes.name: The White Ballot
episodes.overview: Face replaces a candidate who was killed while running for sheriff against a corrupt incumbent, and ends up getting the military after the whole A-Team when his photo is published in the newspaper.

episodes.name: The Maltese Cow
episodes.overview: Old friends who own a restaurant sponsored by the A-Team face an extortion threat from a Chinese tong.

episodes.name: In Plane Sight
episodes.overview: The A-Team employs a new method to prepare B.A. for a flight to South America, where drug smugglers are holding an innocent pilot prisoner.

episodes.name: The Battle of Bel Air
episodes.overview: The A-Team must rescue an employee of a security firm after she warns them about an ambush.

episodes.name: Say It With Bullets
episodes.overview: A WAC asks the A-Team to investigate the death of her brother, who was involved in arms trafficking at a military base.

episodes.name: Pure-Dee Poison
episodes.overview: The A-Team helps a southern minister stop the manufacture of lethal moonshine.

episodes.name: It's a Desert Out There
episodes.overview: The sophisticated commando tactics used by a gang for robbing busloads of tourists suggests to the A-Team that they're preparing for a bigger score.

episodes.name: Chopping Spree
episodes.overview: The A-Team uses their own vehicles, Face's Corvette and B.A.'s van, as bait for a car-stealing ring.

episodes.name: Harder Than It Looks
episodes.overview: The rescue of a kidnapping victim looks easy until the ransom is left behind and the victim insists on bringing along one of her captors.

episodes.name: Deadly Maneuvers
episodes.overview: Criminals foiled in the past by the A-Team hire a crew of mercenaries to pick off each member one by one.

episodes.name: Semi-Friendly Persuasion
episodes.overview: The A-Team faces an especially challenging mission when their pacifist clients forbid the use of violence against bigots trying to run their community off its land.

episodes.name: Curtain Call
episodes.overview: The A-Team reminisces (via flashbacks) about an injured Murdock as they look for a doctor and try to avoid a pursuing Decker.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: Pile into that famous black van for another season of adrenaline-pumping adventure with Hannibal, Face, Murdock and B.A. as they fight for justice against dangerous criminals, while staying one step ahead of their archenemy, Colonel Decker.

episodes.name: Bullets and Bikinis
episodes.overview: Two girls ask the A-Team to take over their beachfront hotel after an alleged mobster keeps making bigger and bigger buyout offers that they refuse to take.

episodes.name: The Bend in the River Part 1
episodes.overview: Tawnia asks the A-Team to find her fiancÃ©, an archaeologist last seen on an Amazon expedition that was attacked by a pirate.

episodes.name: The Bend in the River Part 2
episodes.overview: Tawnia asks the A-Team to find her fiancÃ©, an archaeologist last seen on an Amazon expedition that was attacked by a pirate.

episodes.name: Fire
episodes.overview: The A-Team faces another Army pursuit as they try to help a small town fire chief compete with a larger rival company.

episodes.name: Timber!
episodes.overview: The A-Team intercedes when a union organizer tries to put a small logging operation out of business.

episodes.name: Double Heat
episodes.overview: The A-Team is called in to find an accountant's daughter who has become a pawn in a game between two rival mobsters.

episodes.name: Trouble on Wheels
episodes.overview: Hannibal goes undercover in order to investigate employee theft from an auto plant.

episodes.name: The Island
episodes.overview: An Army doctor who once saved B.A.'s life calls in his debt by asking the A-Team to help deal with the thugs who have taken over the tropical island where he has set up a medical practice.

episodes.name: Showdown!
episodes.overview: Col. Lynch stakes out a Wild West show that has been terrorized by a group of A-Team impostors, sure that the real guys won't be able to ignore them.

episodes.name: Sheriffs of Rivertown
episodes.overview: The A-Team travels to South America where they become the law in a town built to house workers of a power plant that has been experiencing a number of fatal accidents.

episodes.name: The Bells of St. Mary's
episodes.overview: Threats from their old record label prompt a singing group who went to school with Face to ask the A-Team for help.

episodes.name: Hot Styles
episodes.overview: Face's latest girl friend is rather ungrateful after the A-Team rescues her from mobsters.

episodes.name: Breakout!
episodes.overview: After being taken hostage by bankrobbers B.A. and Murdock are named as accomplices and put in jail until Decker can come and get them.

episodes.name: Cup A' Joe
episodes.overview: A restaurateur tries to force the owners of a small diner to sell out to him after he arranges for a new freeway off-ramp to be built nearby.

episodes.name: The Big Squeeze
episodes.overview: The A-Team opens its own restaurant to lure a ruthless loan shark who has other restaurant owners terrified.

episodes.name: Champ!
episodes.overview: B.A. goes undercover as a boxer in order to put a drug-trafficking ring out of business.

episodes.name: Skins
episodes.overview: The A-Team travels to Kenya to deal with game poachers who have included a game warden among their kills.

episodes.name: Road Games
episodes.overview: Face infiltrates a gambling ring to clear a man's gambling debts and to save the foster home he runs.

episodes.name: Moving Targets
episodes.overview: A Middle Eastern potentate hires the A-Team to protect his about-to-be-married daughter despite her ideas to the contrary.

episodes.name: Knights of the Road
episodes.overview: The A-Team comes to the aid of an auto mechanic being driven out of business by a ruthless competitor.

episodes.name: Waste 'Em!
episodes.overview: The A-Team discovers a plot to dump toxic waste when they try to protect a man and his blind sister from harassment.

episodes.name: Bounty
episodes.overview: Murdock is kidnapped by bounty hunters that hope to use him as bait to capture the rest of the A-Team. When the Team arrives to rescue him, they find he has fallen in love with a veteranarian that's helped save him.

episodes.name: Beverly Hills Assault
episodes.overview: The A-Team goes uptown and gets involved with an art dealer who has been replacing original paintings with fakes.

episodes.name: Trouble Brewing
episodes.overview: Two sisters ask the A-Team for help when they are pressured to convert their all-natural soda pop bottling plant into a brewery.

episodes.name: Incident at Crystal Lake
episodes.overview: The A-Team's planned fishing vacation at a lakeside retreat is ruined when Decker and his men show up.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: In the most popular season ever, Hannibal, Face, Murdock and B.A. face off against new criminals with the most outrageous schemes yet - from toxic-waste dumping to wild-game poaching to restaurant sabotage.

episodes.name: Judgement Day (1)
episodes.overview: The A-Team goes to Italy to rescue a judge's daughter from mobsters, then must spend the journey home aboard an oceanliner dodging the boys trying to get her back.

episodes.name: Judgement Day (2)
episodes.overview: The A-Team goes to Italy to rescue a judge's daughter from mobsters, then must spend the journey home aboard an oceanliner dodging the boys trying to get her back.

episodes.name: Where Is the Monster When You Need Him?
episodes.overview: The A-Team must make do with movie prop guns against the real things when they are attacked while helping Hannibal and a friend film a low-budget movie in Mexico.

episodes.name: Lease with an Option to Die
episodes.overview: Some muscle men make a big mistake when they try to force B.A.'s momma out of her apartment.

episodes.name: The Road to Hope
episodes.overview: Hannibal poses as a wino to avoid being caught by the Army and stumbles onto a racket that involves killing the derelicts.

episodes.name: The Heart of Rock n' Roll
episodes.overview: Singer Rick James asks the A-Team to help an old rock-and-roll legend whose life in prison has suddenly become very dangerous.

episodes.name: Body Slam
episodes.overview: Hulk Hogan asks his old friend B.A. for the A-Team's help against a mobster who is out to close down a youth center for no apparent reason.

episodes.name: Blood, Sweat and Cheers
episodes.overview: Someone sabotages a car at a regional stock-car race and attracts the A-Team's attention-the car belongs to Hannibal's nephew.

episodes.name: Mind Games
episodes.overview: Face quits the A-Team after receiving a full government pardon and quickly becomes a celebrity, the rest of the A-Team keeps an eye on him suspecting the pardon's not 100% legit.

episodes.name: There Goes the Neighborhood
episodes.overview: The A-Team moves a rock star threatened with kidnapping into a quiet suburban neighborhood, which doesn't stay quite for long.

episodes.name: The Doctor Is Out
episodes.overview: The A-Team travels to South America to find Murdock's psychiatrist, accompanied by a woman claiming to be his daughter.

episodes.name: Uncle Buckle-Up
episodes.overview: The A-Team discovers a kiddie show is a front for a heroin ring when Hannibal auditions for a part.

episodes.name: Wheel of Fortune
episodes.overview: Murdock's fortunes rise and fall as he uses Face's system to win big on "Wheel of Fortune" but then is kidnapped during a plot to steal a Soviet gunship.

episodes.name: The A-Team is Coming, The A-Team is Coming
episodes.overview: Soviet spys need the A-Teams help in preventing the theft of an American satellite weapon, whose disappearance would disrupt world peace.

episodes.name: Members Only
episodes.overview: Face's chances of getting into an exclusive country club are severely hampered by the A-Team's battles on club property with a crooked bank president.

episodes.name: Cowboy George
episodes.overview: Face believes he's booked country singer Cowboy George into one of the roughest dance halls in the Southwest, but his agent friend delivers Boy George instead.

episodes.name: Waiting for Insane Wayne
episodes.overview: When Murdock gets mistaken for an insane mercenary the A-Team is drawn into a fight over property rights and an oil well.

episodes.name: The Duke of Whispering Pines
episodes.overview: One of B.A.'s old girlfriends has a problem; her husband, B.A.'s old college rival, has disappeared.

episodes.name: Beneath the Surface
episodes.overview: Face returns to his orphanage for a reunion and meets an old friend's sister, who's worried about her brother's disappearance, and an old girlfriend, who is in cahoots with Fulbright to trap Face for the reward.

episodes.name: Mission of Peace
episodes.overview: Senior citizens hire the A-Team to protect their historic Texas mission home and tourist attraction from land developers.

episodes.name: The Trouble with Harry
episodes.overview: Hulk Hogan comes to visit B.A. but the reunion is interrupted by a cry for help from a troubled youth with an alcoholic father.

episodes.name: A Little Town with an Accent
episodes.overview: The A-Team discovers an organized crime kingpin believed to be dead is behind the intimidation of several gas station owners.

episodes.name: The Sound of Thunder
episodes.overview: General Fulbright captures the A-Team then offers to let them prove their innocence by accompanying him to Vietnam and rescuing a POW who could clear their names.

4.name: Season 4
4.overview: Team up again with B.A., Hannibal, Murdock and Face as they take on hardhearted kidnappers, corrupt millionaires, ruthless drug dealers, and even a Mob kingpin.

episodes.name: Dishpan Man
episodes.overview: The A-Team is blackmailed by retired General Stockwell, who kidnaps Hannibal and threatens to have him prosecuted if the A-Team fails to secure the release of hostages held on a plane in Spain.

episodes.name: Trial by Fire
episodes.overview: The A-Team's court martial begins and a surprising motive for the death of Colonel Morrison is revealed.

episodes.name: Firing Line
episodes.overview: General Stockwell interferes with the plans of Murdock and Frankie to free the rest of the A-Team before the Army can execute them.

episodes.name: Quarterback Sneak
episodes.overview: The A-Team uses a football game as a cover to sneak a chemical warfare scientist out of East Germany.

episodes.name: The Theory of Revolution
episodes.overview: The outbreak of a revolution interferes with the planned rescue of three Americans from a Third World Country.

episodes.name: The Say UNCLE Affair
episodes.overview: Stockwell is kidnapped by his former partner who has "gone bad" and the A-Team has 18 hours to find him or forever loose any chances of securing a pardon.

episodes.name: Alive at Five
episodes.overview: Face plans to leave the A-Team but gets involved in the rescue of a newswoman from a paranoid mob chief.

episodes.name: Family Reunion
episodes.overview: A former political adviser offers to trade a diary for a reunion with his daughter- who Face is hitting on, but Murdock learns that the man may be Face's father and the daughter Face's sister.

episodes.name: Point of No Return
episodes.overview: Stockwell refuses to allow the A-Team to go after Hannibal when he fails to check in while on a solo mission in hostile territory.

episodes.name: The Crystal Skull
episodes.overview: The A-Team's effort to secure a valuable religious artifact involves them with warring island tribes who mistake Murdoch for a God and some unusual missionaries.

episodes.name: The Spy Who Mugged Me
episodes.overview: Murdock poses as suave secret agent to catch a killer before he can complete another assignment.

episodes.name: The Grey Team
episodes.overview: The A-Team must bring a girl in who has stolen a briefcase from her father, filled with material she believes he's selling to the Soviets.

episodes.name: Without Reservations
episodes.overview: Frankie and Face visit Murdock at his job in a restaurant, and all three become hostages of mobsters out to kill a patron, the US Attorney General.

5.name: Season 5
5.overview: B.A., Hannibal, Murdock and Face confront their greatest challenges yet when the mysterious General Stockwell joins them to battle bad guys that include hitmen, hijackers, and mercenary monks.
